{"tid":2125378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭錦滿收選舉主任信件　追問四年前港獨言論","createTime":"2020-07-26T07:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T07:12:17.000Z","uid":312744,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c69963a7d07e9f018fc15cb7b3c44e687d862690","tid":2125378,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/HKLegCo/2997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKLegCo%2F2997&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLrO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=49cf7833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKLegCo/2997</a><br />\n<br />\n多名非建制派候選人已經先後報名參與 9 月立法會選舉，選舉主任在昨日（25 日）向多名候選人發信，詢問他們是否真誠擁護《基本法》。在香港島區參選名單排第二、已簽署參選確認書的「熱血公民」鄭錦滿表示，昨日亦收到香港島地方選區選舉主任黃智華來信，追問他於 2016 年發表有關「繼續支持港獨」、提倡「香港建國」等言論，要求他回答是否同意中國擁有香港主權、香港和中國是否有相等的主權國家地位等。選舉主任要求鄭錦滿在今日（26 日）下午 5 時 30 分之前回覆。<br />\n<br />\n鄭錦滿是與《熱血時報》網台主持、綽號「法子」的莊芷茵合組名單，出戰立法會港島區直選。不過排名單首位的「法子」，暫未收到選舉主任查詢。<br />\n<br />\n對於鄭錦滿曾在四年前公開表示「撐『港獨』」言論，選舉主任在信中提問：「請問你是否同意中華人民共和國擁有香港特別行政區主權？」、「請問你是否同意香港特別行政區是中華人民共和國不可分離的一部分？」，並要求他回答是否仍然繼續支持該等主張。<br />\n<br />\n老師、點答好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8b1cc208cf35b8378be36ab9727da400bcb52c","tid":2125378,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjYXNhf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjYXNhf.jpg&h=86cdf8c9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老師 幾年前就幫咗佢答呢個問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8ad347c6d00986aeec74bf20e81a36e8b56049","tid":2125378,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa8b1cc208cf35b8378be36ab9727da400bcb52c","tid":2125378,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjYXNhf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjYXNhf.jpg&h=86cdf8c9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老師 幾年前就幫咗佢答呢個問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇咗老師<br />\n完全係香港人嘅損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b82388586353ca6d39d67153a49a3bd294d7b92","tid":2125378,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:06:31.000Z","msg":"無人想理<br />\n屌你老母四眼狗"},{"pid":"c27cf1add7dbcc5c06989d43927ce2221dc3d656","tid":2125378,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"熱血公民 可以代表我 可以為我永續基本法<br />\n假使可以 五區當選<br />\n錦滿會打交 松泰負責投下反對票<br />\n這樣議事很足夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}